  "text": "In this paper we have explored the impact of tree-level amplitude relations in multiloop integrand computations. There were two major aspects to our work. Firstly, we exploited the Kleiss-Kuijf relations to find a compact colour decomposition for the two-loop amplitude in terms of multi-peripheral colour factors in an analogous way to the tree-level and one-loop decompositions of Del Duca, Dixon and Maltoni [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
